# Resend (https://resend.com) — powers the /contact page email form.
# 1. Create a Resend account and API key.
# 2. Verify a sending domain (or use the onboarding@resend.dev test sender for now).
# 3. Copy this file to .env.local and fill in the values below.
RESEND_API_KEY=
CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=
CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL="Cake House Website <onboarding@resend.dev>"
